Title: EFFICIENCY IMPROVEMENT BY LATTICE RULES FOR PRICING ASIAN OPTIONS  
Author: Christiane Lemieux and Pierre L'Ecuyer 
Address: Montreal, C.P. 6128, Succ. Centre-Ville Montreal, H3C 3J7, CANADA  
Affiliation: Departement d'Informatique et de Recherche Operationnelle Universite de  
Abstract: This paper compares Monte Carlo methods, lattice rules, and other low-discrepancy point sets on the problem of evaluating asian options. The combination of these methods with variance reduction techniques is also explored. 
